<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc9dbf717-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s422k"><num value="422k">§ 422k.</num><heading> Supplement to Federal reclamation laws; short title</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter shall be a supplement to the Federal reclamation laws and may be cited as the Small Reclamation Projects Act of 1956.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc9dbf718-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-06/ch972/s11">Aug. 6, 1956, ch. 972, § 11</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70/1047">70 Stat. 1047</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idc9dbf719-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idc9dbf71a-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idc9dbf71b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">The Federal reclamation laws, referred to in text, are defined in <ref href="/us/usc/t43/s422b">section 422b of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
